videos.headline: Northwestern St. strikes first vs. LSU with short TD
videos.description: Northwestern State QB Shelton Eppler unleashes a strike to Quan Shorts for a 17-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-play (Northwestern St. strikes first vs. LSU with short TD) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: LSU RB Edwards-Helaire dances his way into end zone
videos.description: LSU RB Clyde Edwards-Helaire bounces and dances around defenders for a 4-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (LSU RB Edwards-Helaire dances his way into end zone) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Burrow evades pressure, throws TD pass
videos.description: LSU QB Joe Burrow is able to manage the  pressure as he fires a 14-yard dart to Terrance Marshall Jr. for a TD.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-play (Burrow evades pressure, throws TD pass) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: LSU's defense leaves man wide open for TD
videos.description: Northwestern State QB Shelton Eppler finds WR David Fitzwater wide open for a 26-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-play (LSU's defense leaves man wide open for TD) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Edwards-Helaire powers through for 2nd TD
videos.description: LSU RB Clyde Edwards-Helaire plows through the line for another touchdown making it 24-14.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-play (Edwards-Helaire powers through for 2nd TD) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Burrow keeps it himself for 5-yard score
videos.description: Joe Burrow takes the snap and runs it into the end zone for a 5-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Burrow keeps it himself for 5-yard score) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Burrow threads the needle, hits Marshall for TD
videos.description: Joe Burrow's pass gets through the grasp of a defender and finds Terrace Marshall Jr. for a 6-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Burrow threads the needle, hits Marshall for TD) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: LSU's Palmer skips into end zone on punt return TD
videos.description: LSU's Trey Palmer catches the punt in stride and carves through the defense en route to a 54-yard touchdown return.

videos.headline: Burrow comes alive for another LSU win
videos.description: Joe Burrow throws for 373 yards and two touchdowns, while running for another score in LSU's dominant win vs. Northwestern State.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Burrow comes alive for another LSU win) 2019/9/14 ESHEET SOTFULL
